Name: Dankuusen
Desc:
Dashes forward, attacking multiple enemies in his path. Use immediately after Shouryuusen to move toward airborne enemies. The 5th step in the 8-step Battoujutsu Combo sequence.
Chainable Skills: Shouryuusen, Surging Blade, Sweeping Sword, Whirlwind Cut, Sanrenzan, Hitokiri Strike, Falcon Dive and Rising Slash
